The buggy code has this structure:
```java
if (parent.isFor() && !NodeUtil.isForIn(parent)) {
  if (parent.getFirstChild().getNext() != n) {
    recordDepScope(recordNode, ns);
  } else {
    recordDepScope(nameNode, ns);
  }
} else {
  recordDepScope(recordNode, ns);
